nt-weight:400;\"><span style=\"color: #fff;font-size: 11px;font-family: Verdana, Geneva, DejaVu Sans,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"padding:4px 4px 4px 6px;background: #555;border-top-left-radius: 4px;border-bottom-left-radius: 4px;\">stars</span><span style=\"padding: 4px 6px 4px 4px;background: #007ec6;border-top-right-radius: 4px;border-bottom-right-radius: 4px;\">21</span></span></a><!--TRACK_AWESOME_REPO_ITEM_START____{\"type\":\"repo\",\"stargazerCount\":21,\"repo\":\"paulpflug/script-runner\"}____TRACK_AWESOME_REPO_ITEM_END--> - Simple task runner with a terse syntax.</li>","updatedAt":"2016-09-07T20:00:06.000Z"},{"categoryHTML":"<h2>Task Runners</h2>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://github.com/mysticatea/npm-run-all\">npm-run-all</a><a data-role=\"trackawesomelist-badge\" href=\"https://github.com/mysticatea/npm-run-all\" style=\"text-decoration:none;top: -2px;position: relative;margin-left:4px;margin-right:4px;font-weight:400;\"><span style=\"color: #fff;font-size: 11px;font-family: Verdana, Geneva, DejaVu Sans,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"padding:4px 4px 4px 6px;background: #555;border-top-left-radius: 4px;border-bottom-left-radius: 4px;\">stars</span><span style=\"padding: 4px 6px 4px 4px;background: #007ec6;border-top-right-radius: 4px;border-bottom-right-radius: 4px;\">4.1k</span></span></a><!--TRACK_AWESOME_REPO_ITEM_START____{\"type\":\"repo\",\"stargazerCount\":4142,\"repo\":\"mysticatea/npm-run-all\"}____TRACK_AWESOME_REPO_ITEM_END--> - Fully featured task runner.</li>","updatedAt":"2016-09-07T20:00:06.000Z"},{"categoryHTML":"<h2>File Watchers</h2>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://github.com/Qard/onchange\">onchange</a><a data-role=\"trackawesomelist-badge\" href=\"https://github.com/Qard/onchange\" style=\"text-decoration:none;top: -2px;position: relative;margin-left:4px;margin-right:4px;font-weight:400;\"><span style=\"color: #fff;font-size: 11px;font-family: Verdana, Geneva, DejaVu Sans,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"padding:4px 4px 4px 6px;backgrou